==Starting off==
* '''Doric:''' Hello traveller, what brings you to my humble smithy?
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|I wanted to use your anvils.}}
** '''Player:''' I wanted to use your anvils.
** '''Doric:''' My anvils get enough work with my own use. I make pickaxes, and it takes a lot of hard work. If you could get me some more materials, then I could let you use them.
** {{tselect|Start Doric's Quest?}}
** {{topt|Yes.}}
*** '''Player:''' Yes, I will get you the materials.
*** '''Doric:''' Clay is what I use more than anything, to make casts. Could you get me 6 clay, 4 copper ore, and 2 iron ore, please? I could pay a little, and let you use my anvils. Take this pickaxe with you just in case you need it.
*** {{tcond|If the player does not already have all of the materials:}}
*** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
**** {{topt|Where can I find those?}}
***** '''Player:''' Where can I find those?
***** '''Doric:''' You'll be able to find all those ores in the rocks just inside the Dwarven Mine. Head east from here and you'll find the entrance in the side of Ice Mountain.
***** {{tcond|If the player does not have 15 Mining:}}
****** '''Player:''' But I'm not a good enough miner to get iron ore.
****** '''Doric:''' Oh well, you could practice mining until you can. Can't beat a bit of mining - it's a useful skill. Failing that, you might be able to find a more experienced adventurer to buy the iron ore off.
****** {{tact|continues}}
***** {{tact|end}}
**** {{topt|Certainly, I'll be right back!}}
***** '''Player:''' Certainly, I'll be right back!
***** {{tact|end}}
*** {{tcond|If the player already has all of the materials:}}
**** '''Player:''' You know, it's funny you should require those exact things!
**** '''Doric:''' What do you mean?
**** '''Player:''' I can usually fit 28 things in my backpack and in a world full of quite literally limitless possibilities, a complete coincidence has occurred!
**** '''Doric:''' I don't quite understand what you're saying?
**** '''Player:''' Well, out of pure coincidence, despite definitely not knowing what you were about to request, I just so happened to have carried those exact items!
**** {{tcond|If the player has the exact amounts:}}
***** '''Player:''' In fact, in the exact quantities too!
***** {{tact|continues}}
**** '''Doric:''' Oh my, that is a coincidence! Pass them here, please. I can spare you some coins for your trouble, and please use my anvils any time you want.
**** {{tbox|pic=Copper ore detail.png|You hand the clay, copper, and iron to Doric.}}
**** {{qact|Quest complete!}}
** {{topt|No.}}
*** '''Player:''' No, hitting rocks is for the boring people, sorry.
*** '''Doric:''' That is your choice. Nice to meet you anyway.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|I want to use your whetstone.}}
** '''Player:''' I wanted to use your whetstone.
** '''Doric:''' The whetstone is for more advanced smithing, but I could let you use it as well as my anvils if you could get me some more materials.
** {{tselect|Start Doric's Quest?}}
** {{topt|Yes.}}
*** {{tact|above}}
** {{topt|No.}}
*** {{tact|above}}
* {{topt|Mind your own business, shortstuff!}}
** '''Player:''' Mind your own business, shortstuff!
** '''Doric:''' How nice to meet someone with such pleasant manners. Do come again when you need to shout at someone smaller than you!
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|I was just checking out the landscape.}}
** '''Player:''' I was just checking out the landscape.
** '''Doric:''' Hope you like it. I do enjoy the solitude of my little home. If you get time, please say hi to my friends in the Dwarven Mine.
** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
** {{topt|Dwarven Mine?}}
*** '''Player:''' Dwarven Mine?
*** '''Doric:''' Yep, the entrance is in the side of Ice Mountain just to the east of here. They're a friendly bunch. Stop in at Nurmof's store and buy one of my pickaxes!
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|Will do!}}
*** '''Player:''' Will do!
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|What do you make here?}}
** '''Player:''' What do you make here?
** '''Doric:''' I make pickaxes. I am the best maker of pickaxes in the whole of Gielinor.
** '''Player:''' Do you have any to sell?
** '''Doric:''' Sorry, but I've got a running order with Nurmof.
*** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
*** {{topt|Who's Nurmof?}}
**** '''Player:''' Who's Nurmof?
**** '''Doric:''' Nurmof has a store over in the Dwarven Mine. You can find the entrance on the side of Ice Mountain to the east of here.
**** {{tact|end}}
*** {{topt|Ah, fair enough.}}
**** '''Player:''' Ah, fair enough.
**** {{tact|end}}

===Attempting to use his anvils before the quest===
* '''Doric:''' Hey, who said you could use that? My anvils get enough work with my own use. I make pickaxes, and it takes a lot of hard work.
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|Sorry, would it be OK if I used your anvils?}}
** '''Player:''' Sorry, would it be OK if I used your anvils?
** '''Doric:''' If you could get me some more materials then I could let you use them.
** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
** {{topt|Yes, I will get you materials.}}
*** {{tact|above}}
** {{topt|No, hitting rocks is for the boring people, sorry.}}
*** {{tact|above}}
* {{topt|I didn't want to use your anvils anyway.}}
** '''Player:''' I didn't want to use your anvils anyway.
** '''Doric:''' That is your choice.
** {{tact|end}}

===Attempting to use his whetstone before the quest===
* {{tbox|You should probably ask before using that.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Doric without all of the materials===
* '''Doric:''' Have you got my materials yet, traveller?
* '''Player:''' Sorry, I don't have them all yet.
* '''Doric:''' Not to worry, stick at it. Remember, I need 6 clay, 4 copper ore, and 2 iron ore.
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|Where can I find those?}}
** {{tact|above}}
* {{topt|Certainly, I'll be right back!}}
** {{tact|above}}

===Returning with all the materials===
* '''Doric:''' Have you got my materials yet, traveller?
* '''Player:''' I have everything you need!
* '''Doric:''' Many thanks! Pass them here, please. I can spare you some coins for your trouble, and please use my anvils any time you want.
* {{tbox|pic=Copper ore detail.png|You hand the clay, copper, and iron to Doric.}}
* {{qact|Quest complete!}}

